title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VIII - Gibraltar
description:
On Thursday World Update VIII has been released which has the focus on Portugal and Spain. In this video we will fly over Gibraltar to see the all the POI's which have been added to the city. When comparing it with other piece of Spain and Portugal I do think that Gibraltar probably received most point of interests.
